<dl id="n41056b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41056b">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41056b"> 56(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> see him obliquely</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Those who are in love to the Lord from the Lord, see Him directly, therefore they are in the east and the west; but those who are more in wisdom, <mark>see the Lord obliquely</mark> to the right <small> Emanuel Swedenborg, <a name="ESAW" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ESAW"><cite title="source">Angelic Wisdom Concerning the Divine Love</cite></a> (ed. unknown) 125</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
